# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# NEVER COMMIT SUPABASE DATA OR CREDENTIALS
# The anon key can read every booking (RLS is permissive), so the key and any
# data pulled from Supabase — customer names, balances, GDX records — must stay
# local. This applies to the whole repo.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
.env
*.env
!.env.example
**/.env

# The one-time data-load script has your full per-departure costs/margins.
# It goes into Supabase from your local copy - never into this public repo.
collectives-data-load.sql
*data-load*.sql

# Anything exported/derived from the Supabase booking data (real customer PII)
Collectives - Missing Supplier Costs.csv
*supplier-costs*.csv
*bookings*.csv
*receivables*.csv
*collectives-export*.csv
*collectives-payments*.csv
supabase-*.csv
supabase-*.json
records*.json

# Local tooling & unrelated projects
.claude/
Airasia-Project/

# Local-only readme (GitHub uses README.md)
README - Collectives Dashboard.md

